                Imperator Caesar <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Septi<lb break="no" n="2"/>mius Severus Pius Perti<lb break="no" n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">n</supplied>ax Augustus Arabicus <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">Adi</supplied>abe<supplied reason="lost">nic</supplied>us Parthicus ma<lb break="no" n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">xi</supplied>mus <supplied reason="lost">ponti</supplied>fex maximus tri<lb break="no" n="6"/>bunici<supplied reason="lost">ae pote</supplied>st<expan><ex>at</ex><abbr>is</abbr></expan> VI inpera<lb break="no" n="7"/><supplied reason="lost">tor</supplied> <note>sic</note> XI co<supplied reason="lost">nsul</supplied> II pater patriae <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr><supplied reason="lost">pr</supplied>oco</abbr><ex>n</ex>s</expan>(ul) et <supplied reason="lost">I</supplied>mperator Caesar <lb n="9"/><supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan></supplied> Aurelius Antoninus Augus<lb break="no" n="10"/>tus tribuniciae potesta<expan><ex>ti</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> II <lb n="11"/><supplied reason="lost">e</supplied>t <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublius</ex></expan></supplied> Septim<expan><ex>i</ex><abbr>us</abbr></expan> <del rend="erasure">[Geta</del>] Caesar <lb n="12"/><supplied reason="lost">r</supplied>estituerunt p<supplied reason="lost">er</supplied> Quintum <lb n="13"/>Tineium Sacerdotem <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>atum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustorum</ex></expan> <lb n="14"/>pro praetore a Niceae <note>sic</note> <lb n="15"/>XXXII </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <supplied reason="lost">Αὐ</supplied>τοκράτωρ Κ&amp;lt;αί=Ε&amp;gt;σαρ Λ(ούκιος) Σεπτίμιος <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">Σεουῆ</supplied>ρος Εὐσεβὴς Πέρτιναξ Σε<supplied reason="lost">β</supplied>αστὸ<supplied reason="lost">ς</supplied> <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">Παρθ</supplied>ικὸς μέγιστος ἀρχιερεὺς μέγιστος <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">δημ</supplied>αρχικῆς ἐ